%% Diagram: Notification fan-out — clients use cursor to fetch deltas
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as Client A (writer)
    participant API as API gateway
    participant Meta as Metadata service
    participant Notify as Notification service
    participant CB as Client B (reader)
    participant CC as Client C (reader)

    CB->>Notify: open long-poll / WebSocket<br/>(namespace=N, cursor=12)
    CC->>Notify: open long-poll / WebSocket<br/>(namespace=N, cursor=12)

    CA->>API: commit (file edit, namespace=N)
    API->>Meta: append SFJ row, JID=13
    Meta->>Notify: publish(namespace=N, JID=13)

    Notify-->>CB: hint: namespace=N has updates
    Notify-->>CC: hint: namespace=N has updates

    CB->>API: list_folder/continue(cursor=12)
    API->>Meta: rows where JID > 12
    Meta-->>API: row JID=13
    API-->>CB: changes + cursor=13

    Note over CC: Same flow on CC<br/>(payload contains no file content)
